    "body": "The concrete issue was #20539 when we came up with this general idea. I understand the problem is that Geth crashes and it's not even obvious to the user it happened due to a lack of free file handles. I understand we can be prudent only in some special cases (filesystem, OS). So we could implement this for Linux first -- after all that's the OS the reporter of the linked issue used.",
